data.description: Wonderful 3 bedroom, 2 bath home with loft ready for your personal touch! This great home has been renovated inside & out with new paint (interior & exterior), new flooring, new light fixtures, new hardware, new countertops, new appliances, new bathroom vanity, new, new, new, the list goes on and on and on... With 2,000 square feet of living space, an abundance of natural light, and open floorplan, and an awesome, BIG loft, this home is sure to sell quickly! Call today for a private showing, you won't be sorry!
